726827f-a.title: Queens: Greenpoint Avenue - Van Dam Street
726827f-a.text:
Intersection of Greenpoint Avenue (right) and Van Dam
Street (left), looking east from Review Avenue. Back on
Greenpoint Avenue can be seen St. Raphaels (R.C.) Chureh.
P. L. Sperr  July 27, 1940
NO REPRODUCTIONS
726827f-a.folder: Greenpoint Avenue & Van Dam Street, Queens, NY

726831f-b.title: Queens: Greenpoint Avenue - Review Street
726831f-b.text:
Greenpoint Avenue, east from Review Avenue. View 2 shows the
avenuek intersection with Van Dam Street (left). In the back-
ground is St. Raphaels Roaan Catholic Church, at Hunters Point
Avenue.
July 25, 1939
P.L. Sperr
NO REERODUCTIONS
